Package: proxs3
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, pve-manager (>= 8.0), libhttp-tiny-perl, libjson-perl
Description: S3 storage plugin for Proxmox VE
 ProxS3 provides native S3 storage support for Proxmox VE.
 It consists of a Go daemon (proxs3d) that handles S3 operations,
 caching, and health monitoring, paired with a Perl storage plugin
 that integrates directly with Proxmox's storage subsystem.
 .
 Supported content types: ISO images, container templates,
 snippets, and backups.
